- The integer parameter `mainTank` is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 100.
- The integer parameter `additionalTank` is greater than or equal to 1 and is less than or equal to 100.
- The integer result is the maximum distance that can be traveled by the truck.
- After every 5 liters of fuel consumed from the main tank, if the additional tank has at least 1 liter of fuel, 1 liter of fuel will be transferred from the additional tank to the main tank.
- The truck has a mileage of 10 km per liter.
- The fuel injection from the additional tank to the main tank is immediate and sudden, not continuous.